&lt;h1&gt;Language tricks used&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://stackoverflow.com/a/40560953&quot;&gt;Conditionally add prop to object&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
